#4902
The big cave~
This huge cavern is the headquarters of Legion. The rough stone walls are
covered in graffiti of every type imaginable. The floor is covered in mud,
slime, blood, and who knows what else, sometimes to a depth of a foot. Dead
and rotting corpses are thrown every which way, some of which appear half
eaten. Broken dishes, weapons, and bones are strewn about carelessly.
 
Here and there, you can see goblins in varying states of health, from those
just sleeping to skeletons. Quite a few appear drunk to the world, while
others must be brain-dead from either alcohol or repeated beatings.
 
Staring at all this, the thought comes to you, "Did I miss the party?"
~
