#4903
The slime pit~
This bowl-shaped room sinks to about 2 feet below the outer edges. This
depression is completely filled with some sort of ooze. The smell rising
from the gunk is horrendous, nauseating, and oh so sweet! You wade in and
find a place not occupied, or throw someone out of the way, and settle down
into the putrid slime, until just your head is above the top layer of scum.
Instantly, your body starts to tingle as the slime seeps into your pores,
healing your shattered bones and cut body, mending the punishment you've 
taken from monsters, enemies, and most of your immediate family.
 
Life couldn't get any better.
~
